{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "3.160", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "3.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "4.960", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "4.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "5.760", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "5.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "7.560", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ein paar Zahlen f\u00fcr Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "7.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "16.480", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Unter der schwarz gef\u00fchrten Landesregierung in Th\u00fcringen wurden keine 60\u00a0Millionen Euro in einer Legislaturperiode f\u00fcr Schulsanierungen bereitgestellt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "16.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "22.120", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir stellen in dieser Legislaturperiode \u00fcber 200\u00a0Millionen Euro f\u00fcr die Schulsanierung bereit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "22.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "28.720", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da Sie die Baubeh\u00f6rden derma\u00dfen geschr\u00f6pft haben und dort abgebaut haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "28.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "31.200", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist es dem Bundesland Th\u00fcringen nicht mehr m\u00f6glich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "31.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "32.960", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Planungen so schnell durchzuf\u00fchren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "32.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.320", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die zus\u00e4tzlichen Bundesmittel innerhalb eines halben Jahres h\u00e4tten mitverbaut werden k\u00f6nnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.160", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Aber ich versichere Ihnen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "39.880", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir werden sie in dieser Wahlperiode noch sicher in den Schulen unterbringen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "39.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "40.720", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der zweite Punkt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "40.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.440", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.320", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Th\u00fcringer Landesregierung macht nichts.\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "48.120", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Mittel f\u00fcr Forschung und Technologie sind im Bund um 3\u00a0Prozent aufgewachsen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "48.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das ist sehr gut. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.880", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Th\u00fcringen steigert die Mittel f\u00fcr seine Hochschulen j\u00e4hrlich um 4\u00a0Prozent\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.560", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "verbindlich bis 2019 festgelegt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "56.760", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist eine Leistung."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "56.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.800", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Kollege, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.520", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Lehrermangel angeht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.160", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "stimme ich Ihnen vollkommen zu: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "65.920", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "In allen Bundesl\u00e4ndern in der Bundesrepublik fehlen Lehrerinnen und Lehrer. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "65.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "67.280", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Jetzt frage ich Sie: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "67.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.560", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie lange braucht man f\u00fcr die Ausbildung von Lehrerinnen und Lehrern? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "75.480", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sind in Th\u00fcringen jetzt seit dreieinhalb Jahren in der Landesregierung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "75.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.920", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Lehrerausbildung haben wir hochzufahren versucht. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.720", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Leider schaffen wir es bei f\u00fcnf Jahren Ausbildungszeit nicht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.720", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Vers\u00e4umnisse aus den 24\u00a0Jahren Ihrer Lehrerausbildungspolitik so schnell zu beseitigen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "87.280", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "M\u00f6chten Sie antworten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "87.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "88.520", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kollege Schipanski?\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "88.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.440", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist nicht der Fall."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "95.760", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dann erteile ich das Wort der Kollegin Dr.\u00a0Manja Sch\u00fcle f\u00fcr die SPD-Fraktion."
   ]
  }
 ]
}